snippet.title: Forest Cafe Simulator - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
[WARNING: Either out of laziness or clear-as-day low-budget nature of many Nostra Games titles, the game uses AI generated images for the title screen, trophy icons, PlayStation Store banner, icon and menu image. The game itself, however, doesn't use any AI generated content, thankfully.]

It's time to take care of cute animals and build a cozy cafe for them in a forest clearing. Get everything ready for the reception. Add various tasty dishes and drinks to the menu.

Set the work so that no one has to wait in line for too long, or the animals will get upset. Hire and train staff. Make your cafe the most popular in the forest!

Developed by NOSTRA GAMES
Also released on PlayStation 5 and Nintendo Switch

#ps4 #playstation4 #theforeseenarcade #forestcafe #forestcafesimulator #nostragames
